RawLine: TNPC_20061006,還沒找著不代表沒有，這前朝之大，不可能沒私藏寶藏，{p}所以妽兒深信寶藏存在著，想找到再佔為已有。,还没找着不代表没有，这前朝之大，不可能没私藏宝藏，{p}所以妽儿深信宝藏存在着，想找到再占为已有。

Items.mt: The fact that it has not been found does not mean that it does not exist. The former dynasty was so big that there could not be a private treasure, so the Chinese people are convinced that the treasure exists and want to find it and take it for themselves.
